OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FFour men from Rhyl have appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt after being charged in
OL,8,Fconnection with the sexual
OL,9,Fexploitation of three teenage girls
OL,10,Fover a period of two years.
OL,12,FIt is the prosecution's case that the
OL,13,Fgirls, aged 16 and under, were
OL,14,Ftargeted by Mustafa Iqbal, Mohamed
OL,15,FArshad, Ziaullah Badshah and Jaswinder
OL,16,FSingh, who acted as a grooming gang
OL,17,Fand used the teens as "sexual
OL,18,Fplaythings", plying them with drink
OL,19,Fand drugs before sexually abusing them.
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@KO]
