OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776780668
OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FA fifth defendant, Sarah Gray from
OL,7,FFlintshire is charged with Perverting
OL,8,Fthe course of justice, assisting an
OL,9,Foffender, conspiracy to supply cocaine
OL,10,Fto another, and conspiracy to supply
OL,11,Fcannabis to another.
OL,13,FThe defendants deny all the charges
OL,14,Fagainst them.
OL,16,FJurors at Caernarfon Crown Court have
OL,17,Fbeen told Child B and C were walking
OL,18,Fthrough Rhyl late one spring evening
OL,19,Fin 2022 when they were spotted by
OL,20,Ftakeaway driver Mustafa Iqbal.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
