OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776780668
OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FProsecuting barrister Owen Edwards KC
OL,7,Fsaid Iqbal, 43, quickly concluded the
OL,8,Fpair were "ripe for sexual
OL,9,Fexploitation".
OL,11,FHe added: "These men treated the girls
OL,12,Fas sexual commodities. They took full
OL,13,Fsexual advantage."
OL,15,FIt is claimed the four men in the dock
OL,16,FMustafa Iqbal, Mohamed Arshad,
OL,17,FZiaullah Badshah and Jaswinder Singh
OL,18,Fwere "friends who shared details of
OL,19,Fwhat they could get the girls to do"
OL,20,Fin exchange for drugs.
OL,26,@pD@KOUqD@MO]sD@KOUzD@FOU{D@dO]
