OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FArrests were made when one of the
OL,7,Falleged victims - Child B, a 15-year-
OL,8,Fold, was taken to London by defendant
OL,9,FJaswinder Singh and told to pretend to
OL,10,Fbe his 22-year-old carer.
OL,12,FThe 65-year-old ordered her to do this
OL,13,F"to avoid his sister concluding he was
OL,14,Fpart of an Asian grooming gang".
OL,16,FHowever, upon meeting Child B, another
OL,17,Fgirl quickly decided she needed
OL,18,Fprotection and the prosecution say
OL,19,F"her intervention and that of her
OL,20,Fmother got police involved".
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@_O]{D@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
