OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FIt is the prosecution's case that a
OL,7,Fthird alleged victim, Child A, was
OL,8,Fgroomed by Iqbal and used as a "sexual
OL,9,Fplaything".
OL,11,FOwen Edwards KC said she was
OL,12,Fhandcuffed and raped. She eventually
OL,13,Fwent to police which led to the
OL,14,Fprosecution of all five in the dock.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@JO]
