PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776780668
OL,3,CFour men appear in court as child
OL,4,Csexual exploitation trial begins
OL,6,FThe fifth defendant, 53-year-old Sarah
OL,7,FGray, of Gronant, is accused of
OL,8,Fallowing Iqbal to use her home as a
OL,9,Fsafe house to sexually exploit Child
OL,10,FA. It was also claimed she washed
OL,11,Fbedding following an allegation of
OL,12,Frape. She denies the allegations.
OL,14,FThe trial continues at Caernarfon
OL,15,FCrown Court and could last up to nine
OL,16,Fweeks.
